		<title>5 Ways to Actually Enjoy Editing Your Book</title>
		<link>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/12/editing-your-book.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/12/editing-your-book.html#comments</comments>
