		<title>Don’t Let This Sloppy Technique Kill the Tension in Your Story&#8217;s Climax</title>
		<link>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/11/storys-climax-2.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/11/storys-climax-2.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 26 Nov 2014 11:00:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[K.M. Weiland &#124; @KMWeiland]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Novel Endings]]></category>
