		<title>What Is the Role of Theme in a Story&#8217;s Climax?</title>
		<link>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/11/storys-climax.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.helpingwritersbecomeauthors.com/2014/11/storys-climax.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 23 Nov 2014 11:00:26 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[K.M. Weiland &#124; @KMWeiland]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Theme]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[character arc]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[characters]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[climax]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ending]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[plot]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[the lie your character believes]]></category>
